{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_35","type":"agent_message","text":"I’ve narrowed it down further: `log4j.dtd` is definitely missing from library resources, the Chainsaw/AWT path is missing JNI coverage for `sun.java2d` classes, and the `EnhancedThrowableRenderer` failure looks like a native-image class loading/service-loader behavior difference rather than a direct missing registration. I’m checking whether the repo already treats that pattern as unsupported in native mode before I decide whether to patch metadata only or also tighten the test expectation."}}
